  "Description": {
    "English": "A critical starship safety feature, vital for extra-orbital flight.<br><br>The pressuration capsule is a dedicated unit that both ensures a <span class=\"name name-stellar\">breathable atmosphere</span> and prevents the catastrophic explosion of unconventional cockpit designs.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一项关键的飞船安全功能，对于轨道外飞行至关重要。<br><br>专门安装的增压胶囊将能够维持飞船内部的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">可呼吸大气环境</span>，并避免因非常规驾驶舱设计导致的灾难性爆炸事故。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "舉足輕重的太空船安全構件，對外軌道飛行起了至關重要的作用。<br><br>加壓膠囊是一款專門元件，既能確保<span class=\"name name-stellar\">可呼吸空氣環境</span>，也可預防非傳統式駕駛艙發生災難性爆炸。"
